{"_path":"/travel/v002","_dir":"travel","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"各國電源差異","description":"旅遊指引 - 電源差異","image":null,"sequence":2,"category":"1.旅遊須知","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"旅行導遊"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-09-11T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"旅遊指引-電源差異"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"旅遊指引 - 電源差異"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"各國用電及插頭型態"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"各國用電及插頭型態"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.moztech.cc/blogs/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%92%E9%A0%AD%E5%A0%B1%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5-%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"出國插頭報你知！旅行世界各國要怎麼用電？"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v002-01.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v002-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"台灣熱門旅遊地-電壓"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"台灣熱門旅遊地 電壓"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"日本 100V"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n台灣人最愛的去日本，和台灣很像，所以不用轉接頭與變壓器，只是日本的電壓稍低，只有 100V，所以你會覺得充電較慢，旅遊時最好多留一點時間讓 3C 產品充電，或是帶上行動電源，預防缺電危機！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中國 220V（需準備變壓器＋轉接頭）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n中國的插座有三種長相，且電壓是 220V，與台灣電器的 110V 不同，一定帶變壓器！免得電壓過大，直接燒壞掉...有的產品是支援 110V-240V，如果是這種的就無需準備變壓器，只需自備轉接頭即可，出行前可以先檢查下。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港、英國 220V-230V（需準備變壓器＋英規轉接頭）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n香港和英國是一樣的，採用英規插孔，要注意香港和中國一樣是 220V，英國則是 230V，所以要自備變壓器和轉接頭！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"韓國、歐洲 220V-230V（需準備變壓器＋歐規轉接頭）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n韓國電壓一般爲 220V，歐洲多數國家的電壓都在 220V-240V 這個區間，採用的是歐規插頭，前往時要自備變壓器與轉接頭喔！值得議題的是，韓國多數飯店也會配有 110V 的插座，如果事先詢問清楚，也許有機會可以少帶一點行李。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"泰國、越南 220 V（需準備變壓器＋歐規轉接頭）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n泰國和越南電壓都是 220 V，且有兩種型態的插座，一個是扁型一個是圓腳，插座幾乎是美規+歐規的合體，基本上台灣帶去的雙腳插座可以直接使用，但還是會建議可以多備著歐規轉接頭，以防不時之需。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"美國 120V"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n美國和台灣很像，不需要轉接頭和變壓器，電壓是 120V，比台灣稍高一點點，不過這在電器的容許範圍內，所以不用帶變壓器與轉接頭。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"旅遊指引-電源差異","depth":2,"text":"旅遊指引 - 電源差異","children":[{"id":"各國用電及插頭型態","depth":3,"text":"各國用電及插頭型態"},{"id":"台灣熱門旅遊地-電壓","depth":3,"text":"台灣熱門旅遊地 電壓"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:travel:v002.md","_source":"content","_file":"travel/v002.md","_extension":"md"}